profile:
Mr. Interlock Landscape & Construction is a professional residential and commercial design and build firm servicing the York Region and Greater Toronto Area communities.
 
With over 30 years of experience in interlocking and paving installations, we help our clients create a distinctive design element that will magnify their homes allure, increase its value while offering a unique look customized to meet their landscape desires.
 
We take pride in providing our clients with original and timeless designs, innovative ideas, quality construction, prompt and professional service, outstanding warranty and seamless flow of project implementation from start to finish.
 
Our construction expertise spans across a variety of materials from natural stone, flagstone, marble to cobblestones, standard pavers, concrete and asphalt.
 
We also specialize in a variety of project types such as driveways, patios, stairs, retaining walls, swimming pools, outdoor kitchenettes, outdoor living spaces, outdoor lighting, outdoor audio and more.
 
Our mission is to enhance and beautify the communities we enter by supplying our clients with a uniquely designed landscape project that adheres to our motto "Do It Once, Do It Right". All while providing our clients with unparalleled service through our consultation, planning and execution resulting in long lasting relationships and an abundance of word of mouth referrals.

profile:
The Anything Guys was founded in 2005 by Tom Rheaume. It has since grown to a strong 10 person team. 
 
Our focus is to supply Ottawa residents with a professional, affordable service that is a one-stop shop for both commercial and residential clients, specializing in pretty much anything! We pride ourselves in our ability to offer a large variety of different household and property related services, big or small, irregular or mainstream, which can be found on our services page. 

This is what you receive with every job you book with us: 
 
Convenience: One number, one main contact and an experienced team to handle most any home and garden renovation and maintenance need. 

Quality Work: Qualified tradesmen who will do the work diligently and to the highest standards
Reliability & Consistency: Good communication is very important to us. If a customer changes the scope of work, we notify them of changes to timelines, schedules and budgets. 

Customer Service: Enjoy a positive experience working with TAG.  

Fair pricing that comes with full Insurance: Our pricing is competitive and we are fully insurued which means you aren't at risk when hiring us for your renovation or landscaping work.

profile:
Yards Unlimited Landscaping is among Ottawa’s premier award-winning landscape contractors that for over 27 years. We have been designing and constructing innovative landscapes of all sizes that display the highest level of workmanship and sensitivity to the natural environment. We work with you to create an outdoor atmosphere that meets your personal needs and reflects your lifestyle. We are experts in hardscapes from elegant stone walkways, stunning wooden decks and shimmering pools, as well as softscapes including creative garden beds, unique hedgerows, orchards and opulent floral displays. Our designers delight in creating the most imaginative and functional landscapes using a wide variety of natural materials and the finest flora and fauna.

We make it our business to provide excellent service to our customers and to provide a positive work environment for our staff. We are proud members in good standing of Landscape Ontario the Better Business Bureau and the Canadian Nursery Landscape Association.

Vision, artistry, sustainable design and meticulous execution are key ingredients for a successful landscape design and build. Give your home the finish it deserves with landscaping from award-winning Yards Unlimited Landscaping!

profile:
Natural Impressions Landscaping is a small eco-landscaping firm that specializes in regenerative and sustainable horticultural practices. Founded in 2009 by owner/operator Andrew Burgess, the company specializes in design, installation and maintenance of various landscapes. Our passion for sustainable living, eco-landscaping, exceptional customer service and quality craftsmanship have made us a favorable company throughout the Ottawa area.   

We are based out of the Gloucester/Leitrim area of Ottawa, Ontario, Canada. (2 minutes from Findlay Creek Village)

While our specialty is sustainable garden design, installations and maintenance, we are certified in a wide range of “green services”. Our services are backed with years of landscape design and installation experience and it shows in the high quality of our work which you can view in our websites portfolio, and our social media sites found on our “Home” page. You can sit back, relax and leave the dirty work to us!

Our Mission: Reduce climate change, increase biodiversity, enrich lives via nature!

Our Vision: Create a healthier city with measurable results!

Core Values: 1: Passion 2: Sustainability 3: Belief 

Slogan: Enriching lives via nature! 

We are extremely active in the landscape community and volunteer our time regularly at the Cancer Survivor’s Park, the Beechwood National Military Cemetery and many other charitable events/organizations. We are proud members of Landscape Ontario and the Better Business Bureau and keep an excellent track record with both organizations. 

Andrew (The owner/operator of Natural Impressions) was part of the Landscape Ontario Ottawa Chapter Board of Directors in 2015. Andrew has helped out on the Education Committee, Day of Tribute Committee, as well as several other events. Andrew graduated from the Horticulture Technician Program at Algonquin College in 2006 and has been heavily involved in the green industry for 14 years. 

Call or email us today!

profile:
Let Me Build Your Dream Garden!

I have over a decade of experience specializing in designing low maintenance perennial gardens and mixed foundation plans, specializing in Japanese, therapeutic, rock/zen, modern and water gardens.

I can design the entire property or re-imagine a problem area. My garden design services are perfect for new home owners or those ready to  make changes to their existing space. 

During your consultation, I will view your current landscaping, listen to your preferences and work with you to develop a vision that meets your lifestyle and your budget.

SERVICES

* Visual schematic of your project plan
* Perennial garden or mixed foundation plans
* Water garden design
* Japanese garden design
* Modern garden design
* Rock / Zen garden design
* Therapeutic garden design
* Deck and patio garden design
* Material lists
* Material sourcing (containers, furniture, fencing, plants, soil, sod, mulch, stone, ornaments, etc). 
* General consultations and advice 
* Coordination with your installation team
